---
layout: layouts/error.njk
title: "Server Error"
description: "Something went wrong on our end. Please try again later."
error_code: 500
permalink: /500.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
noindex: true
---
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center lg:text-left prose">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">
      Oops!
      <span class="block text-2xl mt-2 text-stone-600">Something went wrong</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6">
      We're never gonna give you up,<br/>
      never gonna let you down...
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      But our server just did. Sorry!<br/>
      Head back to the <a href="/">homepage</a> or try again.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start">
      <button onclick="location.reload()" class="btn btn--secondary">
        {% phosphor "arrow-counter-clockwise", "bold", { size: 20 } %}
        Try again
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:col-span-2">
    {% youTube "dQw4w9WgXcQ", "Rick Astley - Never Gonna Give You Up" %}
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm prose text-center lg:col-span-3">
    Think this is a mistake?
    <a href="https://github.com/{{ build.issues.owner }}/{{ build.issues.repo }}/issues/new?labels=bug&title=500+Error+Report" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Report an issue
    </a>
  </p>
</div>
